data.description: One of a kind home located perfectly for a rural experience, still with direct access to major travel and shopping! Sitting on almost 4 flat acres, this sprawling home will impress and delight throughout. Immaculate hardwood floors and stunning stone fireplace greet you instantly when entering the home immediately setting a tone of elegance throughout. Your updated gourmet kitchen awaits and will impress any level cook with stainless steel subzero and JennAir appliances with gas range and double ovens! Continue on to your spacious living room with built in speaker system, cozy marble fireplace, and gorgeous cherry flooring all tying in the sense of hearth and home. No master bedroom would be complete without a walk in ensuite bathroom and jacuzzi tub, and this home certainly doesn't disappoint! A massive workshop behind the home is fully equipped with 220 electric lines and drafting cable. With 5 zoned thermostats, updated filtration system, and new furnace, this home only needs you!
